    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_6_7820-7852",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7820-7852",
      "markText": "原拟派林彪率兵入朝，林彪托病推辞。毛泽东便决定派彭德怀挂帅出战。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7820&rangeEnd=7852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7820&rangeEnd=7852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_6_22134-22189",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "22134-22189",
      "markText": "故意向敌人示弱，还有意丢弃一些破旧枪械。麦克阿瑟果然中计，认为志愿军“装备低劣，怯战败走”，命令部队向北冒进。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22134&rangeEnd=22189",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22134&rangeEnd=22189"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_6_22597-22693",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "22597-22693",
      "markText": "这时，第三十八军第一一三师主力沿小路疾行，不顾美机威胁，以十四小时前进七十公里的速度，于二十八日上午八时到达三所里地区，堵死美九军南撤退路。随后，他们又主动西插龙源里，截断敌人的另一条退路。正",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22597&rangeEnd=22693",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=22597&rangeEnd=22693"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_4_2325-2348",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2325-2348",
      "markText": "胜利者是不能被审判的，凡属胜利了的都是正确的。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2325&rangeEnd=2348",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2325&rangeEnd=2348"
