      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "31694-31740",
      "markText": "我们的经验是：依靠人民，再加上一个比较正确的领导，就可以用我们的劣势装备战胜优势装备的敌人。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31694&rangeEnd=31740",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=31694&rangeEnd=31740"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_12_29959-29996",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "29959-29996",
      "markText": "开始，毛泽东同邓子恢等在对农村形势估计和农业合作化方针上，发生了意见分歧。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=29959&rangeEnd=29996",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=29959&rangeEnd=29996"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_7_29486-29524",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "29486-29524",
      "markText": "一九五三年七月二十七日，朝鲜停战协定在板门店签字，结束了历时三年的朝鲜战争。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=29486&rangeEnd=29524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=29486&rangeEnd=29524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_7_32045-32123",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "32045-32123",
      "markText": "对美国军队，如果不接触它，就会怕它。我们跟它打了三十三个月，把它的底摸熟了。美帝国主义并不可怕，就是那么一回事。我们取得了这一条经验，这是一条了不起的经验。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=32045&rangeEnd=32123",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=32045&rangeEnd=32123"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_3_12838-12911",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "12838-12911",
      "markText": "毛泽东回答说：“我们已经找到新路，我们能跳出这周期率。这条新路，就是民主。只有让人民来监督政府，政府才不敢松懈。只有人人起来负责，才不会人亡政息。",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12838&rangeEnd=12911",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12838&rangeEnd=12911"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_7_32767-32788",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "32767-32788",
      "markText": "一件事不做则已，做则必做到底，做到最后胜利",
      "totalCount": 65,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=32767&rangeEnd=32788",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=32767&rangeEnd=32788"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_14_38138-38228",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "38138-38228",
      "markText": "这一段讲话中提出一些重要的思想，可惜没有深入研究下去，更没有付诸实践。所有制形式过于单一的问题，成为长期困扰中国经济发展的一个症结。这个问题的解决，成为留给后人的一个重大历史课题。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=38138&rangeEnd=38228",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=38138&rangeEnd=38228"
    },
    {
