      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3125-3192",
      "markText": "经过“银元之战”和“粮棉之战”两次交锋，民族资产阶级对中国共产党的治国理财能力有所认识，开始认真考虑要接受中国共产党和人民政府的领导。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3125&rangeEnd=3192",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3125&rangeEnd=3192"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23640912_6_37383-37473",
      "chapterUid": 6,
