      "markText": "长夜难明赤县天，百年魔怪舞翩跹，人民五亿不团圆。 一唱雄鸡天下白，万方乐奏有于阗，诗人兴会更无前。",
      "totalCount": 55,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23640912&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=21328&rangeEnd=21377",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ed032ec07168bb50ed09b74?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=21328&rangeEnd=21377"
